{"tid":161993,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲試過比人包？","createTime":"2017-03-19T02:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T04:53:07.000Z","uid":63913,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41e9f2b171ec68eea662f25894e82afed996236a","tid":161993,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T02:47:25.000Z","msg":"讀完ASSO果個暑假去左間蚊型公司做暑期工，人工好低，但志在消磨時間。<br />\n老闆係個失婚婦人，三十多歲，講野唔正，少少似老左的法拉，加上對波都幾大。佢老公離婚之後留左一大舊錢同兩個仔女比佢。<br />\n咁有次跟佢返深圳睇工廠（一對一），夜晚同佢兩個人一間房，唔小心中出左佢。<br />\n自始之後，就開始左比人包的生活，間唔中會跟佢出去酒店食野，食完就例牌爆房，次次都係佢出錢。之後返深圳睇工廠又會順手執番野。<br />\n<br />\n咁佢又會不時買下野比我，試過買iPhone等貴野。<br />\n<br />\n而種關係到我入大學都維持住，一直到我year two 識左而家個女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n諗番都幾爽，果時又有野食又有西屌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449939b9179c649062dc8e375b1649be8c6a0604","tid":161993,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"🍇🍇🍇<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣身邊啲朋友知唔知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0209e3cc72557a556d20e40470c8b0d901699bc","tid":161993,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:00:29.000Z","msg":"好唔好屌"},{"pid":"32680aeff09afc95fba11e66b313ee4c190cf77b","tid":161993,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好葡萄"},{"pid":"76b87afd65ea5373e36c7075f0a9f2fd6055f5cc","tid":161993,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"樓主好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4746061d9d3ebf9d210be8bf20c34c45d773383b","tid":161993,"uid":10844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:07:59.000Z","msg":"More<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c14de762e07b8b83759d71551b62d3826a9e415","tid":161993,"uid":37080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a91749afcbc1a5f6d7aab16a51fde2fb13319f","tid":161993,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:15:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>🍇🍇🍇<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣身邊啲朋友知唔知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇人知<br />\n<br />\n雖然試過夜晚響公司搞，但都係等冇人先做。<br />\n<br />\n最正係有兩三次上佢屋企做，佢兩個小朋友又響到。佢就叫小朋友響廳玩，話媽媽有公司野要同哥哥入房傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1aa8a48edb825e4b052599291094d0c2b4f5b6","tid":161993,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常人一個<br />\n<br />\n女人狼虎之年，仲要岩岩離婚冇耐，真係好想有男人錫。<br />\n<br />\n咁岩又可能睇中我年青力壯，滿足到佢。"},{"pid":"f7833a630a64685acc38ae4974c9e344022931c5","tid":161993,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:24:24.000Z","msg":"咁撚開心算唔算買賣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f744b0ae1c4870348255062fdca731a223972c","tid":161993,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"老左的法拉即係正唔正？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家仲有冇聯絡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516abe9d80f45fa102c251ebaf53e21e10e11186","tid":161993,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老左的法拉即係正唔正？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家仲有冇聯絡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講野唔正幾得意，但又好有女人味<br />\n<br />\n冇聯絡啦，再keep住咁做好卜街，我同女朋友下年就結婚。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果有得比我卜多次老闆都唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ea215febe28ceef4ec5d4f9e73429cb0b9f8e5","tid":161993,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:20:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老左的法拉即係正唔正？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家仲有冇聯絡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講野唔正幾得意，但又好有女人味<br />\n<br />\n冇聯絡啦，再keep住咁做好卜街，我同女朋友下年就結婚。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果有得比我卜多次老闆都唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥唔肥？"},{"pid":"76693a692003b7af93c3967eaf8e3377a746101c","tid":161993,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:53:19.000Z","msg":"得我講？<br />\n<br />\n竟然冇巴絲分享下？"},{"pid":"e60337a3009dda69bc5d561bd70888c02b56c3c2","tid":161993,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得我講？<br />\n<br />\n竟然冇巴絲分享下？</blockquote><br />\n難過中六合彩啊巴打<br />\n去邊度搵人同你講好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一d都唔葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdfcb96a0aae1cf3f7965ad29b914fd06fe3098","tid":161993,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:37:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得我講？<br />\n<br />\n竟然冇巴絲分享下？</blockquote><br />\nhihi我都好想試下，成日睇啲人講啲艷遇，好懷疑係咪ff"},{"pid":"cc68304f0324f5ede83e31b4ff0f7f3a610f8675","tid":161993,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n點解呢啲事永遠冇我份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇方法識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"